711
00:46:28,377 --> 00:46:31,577
I really admire you for the work you do.

712
00:46:31,657 --> 00:46:33,617
Oh, Jesus. "Admire," what does that mean?

713
00:46:33,657 --> 00:46:34,818
Why are you so difficult

714
00:46:34,858 --> 00:46:36,578
