797
00:50:58,545 --> 00:51:00,225
and everybody else.

798
00:51:00,305 --> 00:51:02,145
I'll try.

799
00:51:02,225 --> 00:51:03,666
Keep in touch.

800
00:52:19,507 --> 00:52:20,707
Jim.

